2>\n\n	<p>Paid listing functionality powered by WooCommerce. Create custom job packages which can be purchased or redeemed during job submission. Requires the WooCommerce plugin.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class="last post-59 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock">\n	<a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/resume-manager/">\n	</a><a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/resume-manager/" class="item">\n		<img width="318" height="222" src="https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/resume-small.png?w=318&amp;h=222&amp;crop=1" class="attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image" alt="resume-small" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class="price"><span class="amount">$39</span></span>\n <a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/resume-manager/">Resume Manager</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Resume Manager is a plugin built on top of WP Job Manager which adds a resume submission form to your site and resume listings, all manageable from WordPress admin.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class="first post-8123 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock">\n	<a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-with-facebook/">\n	</a><a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-with-facebook/" class="item">\n		<img width="318" height="222" src="https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facebook.png?w=318&amp;h=222&amp;crop=1" class="attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image" alt="facebook" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class="price"><span class="amount">$19</span></span>\n <a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-with-facebook/">Apply with Facebook</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Allow candidates to apply to jobs via email using their FacebookÂ profile.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class="post-5046 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock">\n	<a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-xing/">\n	</a><a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-xing/" class="item">\n		<img width="318" height="222" src="https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/xinglogo.png?w=318&amp;h=222&amp;crop=1" class="attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image" alt="xinglogo" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class="price"><span class="amount">$19</span></span>\n <a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-xing/">Apply with XING</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Allow candidates to apply to jobs via email using their XINGÂ profile.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class="last post-730 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock">\n	<a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/bookmarks/">\n	</a><a href="https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/bookmarks/" class="item">\n		<img width="318" height="222" src="https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/bookmarks1.png?w=318&amp;h=222&amp;crop=1" class="attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image" alt="bookmarks" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class="price"><span class="amount">$19</span></span>\n <a hr