(11119, 1, '2016-09-16 09:40:20', '2016-09-16 09:40:20', '\r\n<div class="aboutus-main">\r\n<h3>About Meal Blvd</h3>\r\nWe are always being told what to think and how to act. One realm that this is true for is the dining experience. Meal Blvd is an opportunity to break away from the norm and experience food and community in a new but completely personable way.\r\n<div class="aboutus-img"><img class="img-responsive" src="[themeurl]/images/aboutus-2.jpg" alt="aboutus-2" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="aboutus-bottom">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n\r\nMeal Blvd is simple. It connects a host [someone with a table and food] with a guest [anyone who is looking for a completely unique meal and experience]. Anyone can choose to become a host, upload their menu[s], post pictures of their dining space and culinary works, and set their prices accordingly. Similarly anyone can be a guest, by simply registering a guest can then browse and contact hosts that appeal.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n\r\nWe crave connection. What better way to do so than sharing passion and conversation over the medium of food in our own homes and beloved spaces? Nothing says cozy or unique quite like the home, those spaces that we pour our love and creativity into. Meal Blvd is a new and exciting way to share these spaces so dear to us. Additionally, Meal Blvd provides the framework for totally unique culinary magic to exist. With anyone eligible to provide a menu of their own creation, Meal Blvd connects people over a food experience apart from any that can be found in a restaurant.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'About Us', '.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2016-09-21 13:15:34', '2016-09-21 13:15:34', '', 0, 'http://mealblvd.stagingdevsite.com/dev/?page_id=11119', 0, 'page', '', 0),
