(11166, 1, '2016-09-27 04:42:49', '2016-09-27 04:42:49', '<div class="how-main">\n<h2>How It Works</h2>\nMeal Blvd is in the business of human connection. While we recognize the importance of food and space, what brings these elements to life is the human touch. Meal Blvd facilitates connection between food lovers that want to entertain and those that seek to experience.\n\n</div>\n<div class="how_it_works_sec">\n<div class="how-img-text">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-6 img_sec1">\n<div class="how-img-img wow slideInLeft animated"  data-wow-duration="1000ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"><img class="img-responsive alignleft wp-image-11169 size-full" src="http://mealblvd.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/howitworks-1.png" alt="howitworks-1" width="352" height="283" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-6 how-text-text">\n<h2>1. Browse</h2>\nFlip through our friendly hosts and enchanting spaces. Whatever the occasion, our hosts are looking to provide a dining experience that caters to your needs. Whether you’re in the mood for a mere bowl of soup or an extensive ethnic dish, our diverse selection of hosts will serve your desire.\n\n<a href="[siteurl]/listings">See How a Claimed Listings Looks</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="how-img-text">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-6 img_sec1">\n<div class="how-img-img-right wow slideInRight animated"  data-wow-duration="1000ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"><img class="img-responsive alignright wp-image-11174 size-full" src="http://mealblvd.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/howitworks-2.png" alt="howitworks-2" width="346" height="262" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-6 how-text-text">\n<h2>2. Book a Meal</h2>\nChat with a host to arrange meal plans. It can be last minute meal plans or a momentous event, months in the planning; our hosts are always here to make your dining experience one to remember.\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="how-img-text">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-6 img_sec1">\n<di